[h1] Not enough Adachi [/h1]
This is one of the finest JRPGs of all time but It lacks something crucial: enough Adachi.
You see, in the game Adachi is a Social Link and obviously part of the plot. The problem is that even considering this, [b] his screentime isn't remoteley enough [/b].
Suggestions that would DRAMATICALLY improve the game:

- A new ending where you can marry Adachi and be his wife;
- A new game mode that lets you play as Adachi;
- Adachi hot spings scene every in-game weekend;
- Having a mini-Adachi following you instead of Teddie;
- In-game choice to dump Dojima and let Adachi be Nanako's guardian;
- Every time you go fishing, Adachi is there to chat with you;
- Adachi models and plushies you can display in your room;
- Every character is replaced by Adachi;

Hope this helps!
